   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0210881d-7204-45f6-91be-b182f7c95c3e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Run following commands to setup the environment to run MCP lab"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "0b5caa91-fd83-4072-9f3d-269e0502abad",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "sudo apt update\n",
    "sudo apt install -y python3-pip python3-venv\n",
    "/usr/bin/python3 -m venv ~/.venv_mcp\n",
    "source ~/.venv_mcp/bin/activate\n",
    "pip install \"mcp[cli]\"\n",
    "pip install google-adk\n",
    "pip install litellm"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "9406bf39-58f6-4cb2-8980-5f1653f926dd",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Use following command to launch the MCP server"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "423525d5-2a02-4479-b285-892a0a6c00e5",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "source ~/.venv_mcp/bin/activate\n",
    "cd ~/terminating-the-terminator/21-MCP/\n",
    "python mcp_server/weather_mcp_server.py"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e26e45dc-8d19-410c-b7ec-745ee45870f9",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Launch the chat app built using ADK (in new terminal)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "1871fdcd-a744-4b84-8f39-a668513cfc28",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "source ~/.venv_mcp/bin/activate\n",
    "export OPENAI_API_KEY=\"OPENAI-API-KEY-HERE\"\n",
    "adk web --host \"0.0.0.0\" --port 8080"
   ]
  }
 ],
